AssertionError: 使用空用户名却仍然登录成功
assert not '登录失败（页面未跳转）'
 +  where '登录失败（页面未跳转）' = <bound method LoginPage.is_login_successful of <pages.login_page.LoginPage object at 0x000002C0B75FFB10>>()
 +    where <bound method LoginPage.is_login_successful of <pages.login_page.LoginPage object at 0x000002C0B75FFB10>> = <pages.login_page.LoginPage object at 0x000002C0B75FFB10>.is_login_successful

AssertionError: 记住密码功能未正常工作，既没有预填用户名也没有自动登录
assert False

AssertionError: 错误的密码组合却仍然注册成功
assert not True
 +  where True = <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B769A650>>()
 +    where <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B769A650>> = <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B769A650>.is_registration_successful

AssertionError: 未填写邀请码却仍然注册成功
assert not True
 +  where True = <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B76A3410>>()
 +    where <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B76A3410>> = <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B76A3410>.is_registration_successful

AssertionError: 使用错误的邀请码却仍然注册成功
assert not True
 +  where True = <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B76A7ED0>>()
 +    where <bound method RegisterPage.is_registration_successful of <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B76A7ED0>> = <pages.register_page.RegisterPage object at 0x000002C0B76A7ED0>.is_registration_successful
